One small issue in your production code: `getUserById()` can throw `NullPointerException` here if Lancelot returns null:

```java
log.info("user id : {}", userResponse.getUserId());
```

Safer:

```java
if (userResponse == null) {
    throw new IllegalStateException("User not found: " + userId);
}
```
